{"tid":1318584,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友今日下定決心減肥，有無人可以指點下我朋友，唔該","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T00:58:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"57be7359d836cd0455a406ae727c1138ed67805f","tid":1318584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"我朋友150cm高，131kg <br />\n未減肥時飲食:<br />\n早餐：3碗餐蛋麵<br />\n午餐：兩碟焗豬扒飯<br />\nTea：薯片、朱古力、可樂、公司三文治下午茶餐<br />\n飯餐：雜扒飯+m記足三兩餐加大加雞翼<br />\n宵夜：3碗雲吞麵<br />\n<br />\n一星期跑5至8分鐘步，無其他運動<br />\n<br />\n目標：減脂增肌<br />\n<br />\n肥咗咁多年，我朋友都為健康想減肥，再加上咁肥好難搵女朋友"},{"pid":"153a40450084b548466f54f184566783cbaf6112","tid":1318584,"uid":4423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"你朋友個胃黑洞嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f44b143dcc127463a568a74497b568e72e0435","tid":1318584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"153a40450084b548466f54f184566783cbaf6112","tid":1318584,"uid":4423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"你朋友個胃黑洞嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"份工係體力勞動消耗大所以要食返多啲嘢"},{"pid":"59834f3c936b1d87a895342d52c1c8050800b919","tid":1318584,"uid":258513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"150?堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7f0efd5c5392c73d9cd9842f450896f5fdbc15","tid":1318584,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c752e893410237cd99b44375e2ece0002689cc31","tid":1318584,"uid":257516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"721企前線 包你減到肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7977211c4d69cb9e17041671e0c6b9445e5539","tid":1318584,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"唔食飽 點有力減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e71ed3ef52b4d4f14795fa1c90c9675729570f","tid":1318584,"uid":135475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"跑八分鐘不如唔好跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃自己減咗肥，心靈上好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有效減肥最少要帶氧30分鐘 唔使太chur  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過睇死你個朋友肯定跑完步都瘋狂食嘢<br />\n<br />\n做手術🈹胃先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d934742ca89af1dd5a47b3b442dd7c743dadff4","tid":1318584,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"啲食糧會否太驚人 ?"},{"pid":"082dc08da63cad5c10f3c7c3d462c5528c02fae0","tid":1318584,"uid":4423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"你朋友去游水應該會好過跑步<br />\n佢咁嘅體重好傷膝頭"},{"pid":"6a89e01ffc3a91599bf48b84f32102ed1ebfffdd","tid":1318584,"uid":52062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"早餐：3碗餐蛋麵= 743 x 2 = 1486kcal<br />\n午餐：兩碟焗豬扒飯= 1300 x 2 = 2600kcal<br />\nTea：薯片、朱古力、可樂、公司三文治下午茶餐 = 零食可樂計你1000 + 公司治 660 = 1660kcal<br />\n飯餐：雜扒飯+m記足三兩餐加大加雞翼 <br />\n= 個飯輕鬆過 2000 + m記餐加大加雞翼 1400 = 3400 kcal<br />\n宵夜：3碗雲吞麵 = 500 x 3= 1500kcal<br />\n<br />\n總攝取卡路里= 10646kcal<br />\n計返基礎代謝率, 當你(朋友)30歲, 揀返勞動密集工作, 一日係4000kcal左右......."},{"pid":"a776a44f9217f283d2bb241cd844a9db7a947343","tid":1318584,"uid":269893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57be7359d836cd0455a406ae727c1138ed67805f","tid":1318584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"我朋友150cm高，131kg <br />\n未減肥時飲食:<br />\n早餐：3碗餐蛋麵<br />\n午餐：兩碟焗豬扒飯<br />\nTea：薯片、朱古力、可樂、公司三文治下午茶餐<br />\n飯餐：雜扒飯+m記足三兩餐加大加雞翼<br />\n宵夜：3碗雲吞麵<br />\n<br />\n一星期跑5至8分鐘步，無其他運動<br />\n<br />\n目標：減脂增肌<br />\n<br />\n肥咗咁多年，我朋友都為健康想減肥，再加上咁肥好難搵女朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"所有抗爭都出黎  今日6:30金鐘見！"},{"pid":"1efe91069315b72cec3f71873be06d6e21385d31","tid":1318584,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"假膠都睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28078a3148777b38e7a1d7a3788d9dc29b0d05f","tid":1318584,"uid":177288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"如果唔係派膠<br />\n<br />\n由每餐份量減到一份先<br />\n再慢慢由每餐咁轉番正常健康飲食去到餐餐都健康飲食<br />\n<br />\n運動方面<br />\n太重唔好跑步 傷膝<br />\n游多啲水 由20分鐘開始去到游40分鐘<br />\n減到少少肥先試下緩步跑<br />\n由跑10分鐘開始 慢慢加到30分鐘 再加速 <br />\n然後就aim 10k/1hr"},{"pid":"4879af835272f0d74e099df66853f045300a6a48","tid":1318584,"uid":29312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"150cm高<br />\n131kg?? kg喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n131磅已經係一個波黎 仲要kg..."},{"pid":"a99eb17db0d6f8fff89ab040942d43a05f9fc1cd","tid":1318584,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"我184 最肥果時先130kg<br />\n你150 可以肥到131 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37755e661192a4e277adf597ec1d101c00e239f3","tid":1318584,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"控制一日只食1500卡，唔使做運動包減到"},{"pid":"4fc724215a437ee38ec2454a6eb295a064852b1e","tid":1318584,"uid":57844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"好明顯係膠POST 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efea4bde877a2f1c3d46cdc5315824dd4d52cd51","tid":1318584,"uid":185213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57be7359d836cd0455a406ae727c1138ed67805f","tid":1318584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"我朋友150cm高，131kg <br />\n未減肥時飲食:<br />\n早餐：3碗餐蛋麵<br />\n午餐：兩碟焗豬扒飯<br />\nTea：薯片、朱古力、可樂、公司三文治下午茶餐<br />\n飯餐：雜扒飯+m記足三兩餐加大加雞翼<br />\n宵夜：3碗雲吞麵<br />\n<br />\n一星期跑5至8分鐘步，無其他運動<br />\n<br />\n目標：減脂增肌<br />\n<br />\n肥咗咁多年，我朋友都為健康想減肥，再加上咁肥好難搵女朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n先睇飲食<br />\n<br />\n早/午餐此終有體力勞動，比係我對呢2餐都唔會太限制，不過... (盡量啦)<br />\n<br />\n早餐: 食麥包(有纖維又頂肚)(應該平過餐蛋麵x3)<br />\n<br />\n午餐: 食得多可以... 不過要走汁/少調味/切走脂肪先好食，同埋習慣下食反多的菜(我自己食飯一定食菜食到5成飽先食其他野)<br />\n<br />\n下午茶餐(我自己係:如果唔係蛋白粉配生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)冧都唔好冧<br />\n<br />\n晚餐: 食7成飽(冇調味菜5成/低調味肉2成)，唔比食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宵夜: 請早睡(開完夜就飲少少水去瞓算)(真係肚餓先食一塊麥包)<br />\n<br />\n誡糖份(包括奶茶/咖啡入面)<br />\n誡零食/氣水/果汁(細佬我已經誡左5年)<br />\n誡食10成飽<br />\n誡宵夜(除非係食&rdquo;擦膠雞胸&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n多飲水(好L多)<br />\n<br />\n再睇下運動<br />\n<br />\n切記：卡路里out&gt;卡路里in（因爲工作性質，每日少少就ok)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做體力勞動工其實應該有大把實用嘅肌肉,只需減脂同練下core... 身形會慢慢走出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果放工反屋企要搭車，可以自己試下早1個/2個站落車，行反屋企(快行)，仲有行路試下令自己習慣&rdquo;收腹&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n樓上有位朋友講得啱，有假放真係去游下水，唔洗好激烈，比個心肺習慣下先(做運動習慣)<br />\n<br />\n同埋平時企可開始留意下自己有冇&rdquo;寒背&rdquo;，如果有就算瘦左都唔會好得去邊<br />\n<br />\n自己有時間要拉多啲筋，開工出事機會都少啲<br />\n<br />\n加油加油... 同埋加油<br />\n唔好冧住可以短期搞掂，最緊要養成良好習慣"},{"pid":"daaa557aadfceaa5cdf90060bed556a21f8a6274","tid":1318584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca3af9f1c5e7825e0442b4494e442bfa6654fda","tid":1318584,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b20464fb1cfc236c99989234273f00f52b39889","tid":1318584,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32cacfba4c7ba4dc14feaa2594abd7d729006480","tid":1318584,"uid":121866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"膠味太濃 重作"},{"pid":"f6da90b69c7dbeeef3a1cdbcc271dafdaba0b334","tid":1318584,"uid":246366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"只想知你朋友人工幾多,火食開支幾大my"}]}